sequenceDiagram
    participant Bootloader
    participant Kernel
    participant Memory
    participant Scheduler
    participant Runtime
    participant Audit
    Bootloader->>Kernel: handoff(memory_map, boot_info)
    Kernel->>Memory: initialize frames and page tables
    Kernel->>Audit: start early ring buffer
    Kernel->>Scheduler: create runtime task
    Scheduler->>Runtime: enter init userspace
    Runtime->>Kernel: sys_info / sys_trace_context
    Kernel->>Audit: record runtime start
